reviews.review_text:
Thirteenth Days Between 13/41: Corrina (8:41)->Drumz (37:40)->INAM (4:06)->Days (9:27)->Throwing Stones->Love Light. 

I like this one, I really do. But it fizzles here and there. Not a complete show. Awesome drums/space well worth your time. Hypnotic.
